message.body: I'm letting the guy that won't leave me alone take me out to dinner. He's paying!
I'm going to the hell for sad people. Why can't we be in the same city?

Are you with bri?
I am
Tell her hi :). WHY did megan have to get in a car accident I have too much to talk to you about and it's killing me
